text: There are no mistakes, only lessons to be learned. I did the best I could
I am allowed to express pain
I accept that I am anxious
I realize that my brain is playing tricks on me
I get angry sometimes, but I am full of love
I have let go of any needs to be perfect
I focus on right now
I let go of people who do not have my best interests at heart
I am an observer - without judgment
At this moment, I choose to release the past and look forward to the good that awaits me
At this moment, I choose to feel calm and peaceful. Everything is unfolding as it should
I accept myself and create peace in mine mind and heart
I take a deep breath
I breathe in relaxation, I breathe out tension
I am more and more calm with each deep breath I take
Every cell in my body is relaxed and oozes calmness
My body is calm
I have the power to change my story
I am strong and able to handle anything
I am capable of solving any problems that face me
I have released all doubts and fears
I have released all harmful tension from my mind and body
I am free of jealousy anger irritation and feelings of unworthiness
I am ridding my mind of negative thoughts and filling it with positive ones
The feelings of panic are leaving my body
I am freeing myself from stress
I am relaxing each part of my body
I have the ability to overcome anxiety
My mind is clearing and I am in control
I am safe and in control
I am free of anything that weighs me down
I am attracting positive energy into my body
All is well in my world
I choose peace!
Peace of mind and I are one
I have everything I need for a happy life
Any reason to live no matter how small that reason it is good enough
I have such a bright future!
I decide how my story is told
I accept myself for who I am, in my current state
I have so much to celebrate myself. I have got my back
I cherish the unique person I am
I am blessed to have a wonderful soul
Self belief and faith now flow easily through me
I review a mental victory log to keep my confidence high
I exude poise and self-assurance
I appreciate my life
I am doing the best I can
I believe in my ability to get through tough times. Whatever I manage to do today is enough.
I celebrate everyday wins, big or small
I am blessed
